### Entry Operations Console checklist
### 1) Baseline: home and entries list
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Baseline: list entries
GET http://localhost:3000/entries

### 2) Create entry (form route)
POST http://localhost:3000/entries/new
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

content=Baseline+entry

### 3) API patch success
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/entries/1
Content-Type: application/json

{ "content": "Updated via API PATCH" }

### 4) API patch not-found
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/entries/999
Content-Type: application/json

{ "content": "Missing entry" }

### 5) API delete success
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/entries/1

### 6) API delete not-found
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/entries/999

### 7) Console page load
GET http://localhost:3000/entries/ops

### 8) Create entry for form operations
POST http://localhost:3000/entries/new
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

content=Form+entry

### 9) Form patch check (POST + urlencoded body)
POST http://localhost:3000/entries/ops/patch
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

id=2&content=Updated+via+ops+form

### 10) Form delete check (POST + urlencoded body)
POST http://localhost:3000/entries/ops/delete
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

id=2
